snippet: Mr. Duterte, president of the Philippines, and Prime Minister Najib Razak of Malaysia found time for a few songs at a state dinner, including “Wind Beneath My Wings.”...
abstract: Pres Rodrigo Duterte of Philippines joins Prime Min Najib Razak for round of karaoke during state dinner in Malaysia.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Duterte, president of the Philippines, and Prime Minister Najib Razak of Malaysia found time for a few songs at a state dinner, including “Wind Beneath My Wings.”

headline.main: Rodrigo Duterte Takes Karaoke Diplomacy to Malaysia
